{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji36.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给贺果的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给贺果的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1956年4月29日）培真兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我的信收到了，感谢你的好意。我情况还好。盼你保养身体。便时望将你的情况告我为盼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝健康！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年四月廿九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]贺果，字培真，毛泽东在湖南省立第四师范学校和第一师范学校读书时的同学。当时任贵州省贵阳市教育局局长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":4,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":332,"page_end":332},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}